title._content: James Morris, KOAC program director with satellite dish

description._content: Original Collection: Gwil Evans Photographic Collection (P82) Item Number: P082:035_1525 Image Description: James "Jimmie" Morris received a degree in Electrical Engineering from Oregon Agricultural College in 1928. Morris became a full-time producer and announcer for KOAC in 1932 and served as the Program Director from 1945-1963. Morris retired in 1972.
